U.K. Fund May Buy Alrosa Natural-Gas Assets, Kommersant Says

-- B y   H e n r y   M e y e r
-- 
2011-09-21T04:40:09Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-21/u-k-fund-may-buy-alrosa-natural-gas-assets-kommersant-says.html
British Empire Special Situations
Plc, a U.K. investment fund, may acquire the natural-gas assets
of OAO Alrosa,  Russia ’s diamond mining monopoly, Kommersant
reported, citing a person familiar with the matter.  The U.K. fund is carrying out due diligence scrutiny and
hopes to complete the transaction in February, the newspaper
reported, citing an unidentified official in VTB Capital, which
holds the assets. It’s ready to pay between $1 billion and $1.3
billion, the person said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Henry Meyer in Moscow at 
